Not fake at all, sir. 

It's there, all songs in two mp3 files. Don't blame the seeder if it is so hard for you to understand this simple fact.
Don't have anything against ripping whole albums to one file, but on mp3s it's just pretty stupid fashion since the files can't be cut by cue sheets any way. My 2 cents.
